keyFacts: The document is an official DOJ OIG evidence custody record (Form III-234/I dated 04/23/07).
It documents a property seizure that occurred on May 31, 2007, at approximately 16:00.
The specific property seized, the location of seizure, and the names of the seizing agent and witness are illegible or redacted in the provided text.
The document includes a chain of custody log, indicating standard evidence handling procedures were followed.
